game.name: Fly Car Stunt 2
game.description:
The second version of the popular Fly Car Stunt will remain the fun and thrill. However, the new features of Fly Car Stunt 2 will give you so many reasons to keep you engrossed for hours. It will be a mix of danger and action. Of course, you have to put your driving prowess to the test when you accept the challenge of this brand new racing game. No need to waste your time. All you need to hop on your fast car and gear up to floor the gas like never before.

Common friends! You are alone as the experienced competitors are waiting for you on the tracks. You can beat them by just challenging your driving abilities to the utmost possible level. Choose any option out of two modes including 1-player or the 2-player mode in this HTML5 car game! Reach the finish line first to complete the level when you are playing the solo mode! Plenty of obstacles will be there to handle there. Make sure that your car does not fall off the track during the race.

Invite your friends and see who is the best racer by playing the second mode! The winner will be only the one who has the ability to reaches the finish line first. There are 12 unique and addictive levels to play through for the players. Do not forget to use the nitro to fly and increase your time in the air. Keep your eyes on the obstacles, and keep your car away from the underground nails, electrical shocks, saws, axes and swinging sledgehammers to race without a stop!
